#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn2.21"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn2.21:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 2 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 2 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn2.21:0.2"
msgid "3. Nānātitthiyavagga "
msgstr "3. Various Sectarians "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn2.21:0.3"
msgid "21. Sivasutta "
msgstr "21. With Shiva "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p><span class="evam">
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn2.21:1.1"
msgid "Evaṃ me sutaṃ—"
msgstr "So I have heard. "

#. HTML: </span>
msgctxt "sn2.21:1.2"
msgid "ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme. "
msgstr "At one time the Buddha was staying near Sāvatthī in Jeta’s Grove, Anāthapiṇḍika’s monastery. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn2.21:1.3"
msgid "Atha kho sivo devaputto abhikkantāya rattiyā abhikkantavaṇṇo kevalakappaṃ jetavanaṃ obhāsetvā yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ aṭṭhāsi. "
msgstr "Then, late at night, the glorious god Shiva, lighting up the entire Jeta’s Grove, went up to the Buddha, bowed, stood to one side, "

msgctxt "sn2.21:1.4"
msgid "Ekamantaṃ ṭhito kho sivo devaputto bhagavato santike imā gāthāyo abhāsi: "
msgstr "and recited these verses in the Buddha’s presence: "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn2.21:2.1"
msgid "“Sabbhireva samāsetha, "
msgstr "“Associate only with the virtuous! "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.21:2.2"
msgid "sabbhi kubbetha santhavaṃ; "
msgstr "Try to get close to the virtuous! "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.21:2.3"
msgid "Sataṃ saddhammamaññāya, "
msgstr "Understanding the true teaching of the good, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.21:2.4"
msgid "seyyo hoti na pāpiyo. "
msgstr "things get better, not worse. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts2ed1.130, sc3
msgctxt "sn2.21:3.1"
msgid "Sabbhireva samāsetha, "
msgstr "Associate only with the virtuous! "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.21:3.2"
msgid "sabbhi kubbetha santhavaṃ; "
msgstr "Try to get close to the virtuous! "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.21:3.3"
msgid "Sataṃ saddhammamaññāya, "
msgstr "Understanding the true teaching of the good, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.21:3.4"
msgid "paññā labbhati nāññato. "
msgstr "wisdom is gained—but not from anyone else. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "sn2.21:4.1"
msgid "Sabbhireva samāsetha, "
msgstr "Associate only with the virtuous! "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.21:4.2"
msgid "sabbhi kubbetha santhavaṃ; "
msgstr "Try to get close to the virtuous! "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.21:4.3"
msgid "Sataṃ saddhammamaññāya, "
msgstr "Understanding the true teaching of the good, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.21:4.4"
msgid "sokamajjhe na socati. "
msgstr "you don’t sorrow even among those who sorrow. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts1ed1.57, sc5
msgctxt "sn2.21:5.1"
msgid "Sabbhireva samāsetha, "
msgstr "Associate only with the virtuous! "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.21:5.2"
msgid "sabbhi kubbetha santhavaṃ; "
msgstr "Try to get close to the virtuous! "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.21:5.3"
msgid "Sataṃ saddhammamaññāya, "
msgstr "Understanding the true teaching of the good, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.21:5.4"
msgid "ñātimajjhe virocati. "
msgstr "you shine among your relatives. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc6
msgctxt "sn2.21:6.1"
msgid "Sabbhireva samāsetha, "
msgstr "Associate only with the virtuous! "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.21:6.2"
msgid "sabbhi kubbetha santhavaṃ; "
msgstr "Try to get close to the virtuous! "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.21:6.3"
msgid "Sataṃ saddhammamaññāya, "
msgstr "Understanding the true teaching of the good, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.21:6.4"
msgid "sattā gacchanti suggatiṃ. "
msgstr "sentient beings go to a good place. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc7
msgctxt "sn2.21:7.1"
msgid "Sabbhireva samāsetha, "
msgstr "Associate only with the virtuous! "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.21:7.2"
msgid "sabbhi kubbetha santhavaṃ; "
msgstr "Try to get close to the virtuous! "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.21:7.3"
msgid "Sataṃ saddhammamaññāya, "
msgstr "Understanding the true teaching of the good, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.21:7.4"
msgid "sattā tiṭṭhanti sātatan”ti. "
msgstr "sentient beings live happily.” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p>
#. REF: pts2ed1.131, sc8
msgctxt "sn2.21:8.1"
msgid "Atha kho bhagavā sivaṃ devaputtaṃ gāthāya paccabhāsi: "
msgstr "Then the Buddha replied to Shiva in verse: "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc9
msgctxt "sn2.21:9.1"
msgid "“Sabbhireva samāsetha, "
msgstr "“Associate only with the virtuous! "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.21:9.2"
msgid "sabbhi kubbetha santhavaṃ; "
msgstr "Try to get close to the virtuous! "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.21:9.3"
msgid "Sataṃ saddhammamaññāya, "
msgstr "Understanding the true teaching of the good, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.21:9.4"
msgid "sabbadukkhā pamuccatī”ti. "
msgstr "you’re released from all suffering.”"

#. HTML: </p></blockquote></article></section></body></html>
